{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"niid19z8g3ccte9jwg9z3ts","title":"Citation Key","desc":"","updated":1669492757347,"created":1669491997247,"custom":{},"fname":"zendron.citation-key","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Zendron"},"contentHash":"65916c9aec7cfe8ad6f12d0a21613993","links":[],"anchors":{"extras":{"type":"header","text":"Extras","value":"extras","line":7,"column":0,"depth":2},"autopindelay":{"type":"header","text":"AutoPinDelay","value":"autopindelay","line":8,"column":0,"depth":3},"steps":{"type":"header","text":"Steps","value":"steps","line":12,"column":0,"depth":4},"citation-counts":{"type":"header","text":"Citation Counts","value":"citation-counts","line":18,"column":0,"depth":3},"manual-pin":{"type":"header","text":"Manual Pin","value":"manual-pin","line":22,"column":0,"depth":3},"better-bibtex-automatic-export":{"type":"header","text":"Better BibTex Automatic Export","value":"better-bibtex-automatic-export","line":27,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"xxezmgby3v2mlneka3t295g","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"citation-key\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#citation-key\"></a>Citation Key</h1>\n<h2 id=\"extras\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#extras\"></a>Extras</h2>\n<h3 id=\"autopindelay\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#autopindelay\"></a>AutoPinDelay</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Change <a href=\"https://retorque.re/zotero-better-bibtex/installation/preferences/hidden-preferences/\">AutoPinDelay</a> to automatically pin the citation key (add to extras) upon importing\n<ul>\n<li>Change integer to 1</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"steps\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#steps\"></a>Steps</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>(1) <img src=\"/Parameter_Estimation/assets/images/zendron.citation-key.md.zotero-config-editor.png\"></li>\n<li>(2) <img src=\"/Parameter_Estimation/assets/images/zendron.citation-key.md.zotero-config-editor-accept-risks.png\"></li>\n<li>(3) Search for <code>autoPinDelay</code> and change the integer value from <code>0</code> (default) to <code>1</code>.\n<img src=\"/Parameter_Estimation/assets/images/zendron.citation-key.md.autoPinDelay-update.png\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"citation-counts\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#citation-counts\"></a>Citation Counts</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>This doesn't conflict with <a href=\"https://github.com/eschnett/zotero-citationcounts\">Zotero Citation Count Manager</a>. It just appends the pinned citation key.\n<img src=\"/Parameter_Estimation/assets/images/zendron.citation-key.md.be%20a%20bat%20extra.png\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"manual-pin\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#manual-pin\"></a>Manual Pin</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Highlight the entry and select manual pin to add the citation key to extras\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"/Parameter_Estimation/assets/images/zendron.citation-key.md.manual-pin-citation-key.png\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>This will need to be once after chaning the AutoPinDelay setting to 1</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"better-bibtex-automatic-export\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#better-bibtex-automatic-export\"></a>Better BibTex Automatic Export</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>This is the first version</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"nuyfwd7iokzd7m9oax0cdx5","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1662428184246,"created":1661538521294,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Zendron"},"contentHash":"9185b031f95deeced1275adbefc49c09","links":[],"anchors":{"parameter_estimation":{"type":"header","text":"Parameter_Estimation","value":"parameter_estimation","line":7,"column":0,"depth":2},"paper-export":{"type":"header","text":"Paper Export","value":"paper-export","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["m7o7r4jqe4jdwgsh3ia8sa4","2fib55e8qqux9scimc7a9gn","tz8wfy0bid